name: BetaPro S&P/TSX Capped Energy -2x Daily Bear ETF
longDescription: NRGD seeks daily investment results, before fees, expenses, distributions, brokerage commissions and other transaction costs, that endeavour to correspond to two times (200 percent) the inverse (opposite) of the daily performance of the S and P/TSX Capped Energy Index TM. NRGD does not seek to achieve its stated investment objective over a period of time greater than one day.
